msgid "Logstash"
msgstr "Logstash"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/centralized-log-management.adoc:183
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/centralized-log-management.adoc:273
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/centralized-log-management.adoc:360
msgid "Kibana"
